file.name: Arrays.v1.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Arrays.v1
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3000'
paths:
  /orgs/{orgUuid}:
    get:
      summary: Get org
      tags: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  id:
                    type: string
                    format: uuid
                  name:
                    type: string
                  orders:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        id:
                          type: string
                          format: uuid
                          example: 53f7bd7b-2ee2-4be4-a15b-e09c76a150f9
                        receivedOn:
                          type: string
                          format: date-time
                          example: '2021-11-22T16:37:15.000Z'
                        fulfilledOn:
                          type: string
                          format: date-time
                        isFulfilled:
                          type: boolean
                          default: false
                        orderedTrees:
                          type: string
                          example: '1000'
                        plantedTrees:
                          type: string
                          example: '700'
                        href:
                          type: string
                          format: url
                          example: 'http://localhost:3000/orders/53f7bd7b-2ee2-4be4-a15b-e09c76a150f9.json'
                      required:
                        - id
                        - receivedOn
                        - fulfilledOn
                        - isFulfilled
                        - orderedTrees
                        - plantedTrees
                        - href
                required:
                  - id
                  - name
                  - orders
      operationId: get-org
      parameters:
        - schema:
            type: string
            format: uuid
          name: orgUuid
          in: path
          required: true
components:
  schemas: {}
